{"tid":2516192,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"見到戴祖儀都有手機廣告賣，我當堂嚇一跳","createTime":"2021-05-04T13:15:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T13:40:58.000Z","uid":219969,"like":79,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"177b5da034b41820b660dc37ca6ea8aacce5312f","tid":2516192,"uid":219969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T13:15:13.000Z","msg":"早排見到「後生仔」戴祖儀、游嘉欣有得賣手機廣告，又搞直播打機對決，又整埋明星Stickers Pack，我當堂嚇一跳，然後得啖笑，原來搵佢哋嗰間 <strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">POCO Phone係 小米 旗下手機牌子嚟</span></span></strong>🇨🇳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n🇨🇳 POCO Phone (小米) 🇨🇳<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/POCOHongKongOfficial\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FPOCOHongKongOfficial&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordKyukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=f555fe1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/POCOHongKongOfficial</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://pili.app/pg/T5J2j7DO\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpili.app%2Fpg%2FT5J2j7DO&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordKyukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=03d14799\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://pili.app/pg/T5J2j7DO</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRkQWrXXmBqd5rxiyQc3wcQwZdNS6w4gc1gyv1Q3UwGzz?filename=gDD13tU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgDD13tU.jpg&h=2856241f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家用得開心啲，唔洗預我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//網絡保安專家西里格（Gabi Cirlig）近日向《福布斯》（Forbes）透露，指經他驗證後，自己正被使用的紅米Note 8（Redmi Note 8）手機監控外，還<strong><span class=\"red\">大量收集他的網絡與通話使用數據，送到科技巨頭阿里巴巴託管的遠程伺服器</span></strong>，而這些伺服器表面上是小米租用的。//<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200502/7FGCVRNRYXAKADKIU6ZY255RGA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200502%2F7FGCVRNRYXAKADKIU6ZY255RGA&d=qHuNkoJY